 Shift+F10 to open cmd
 run the following commands directly (or open task manager with command taskmgr):
 
 hostname 
 powershell
 Install-Script -Name Get-WindowsAutoPilotInfo
 Set-ExecutionPolicy unrestricted
 cd "C:\Program Files\WindowsPowerShell\Scripts\"
 .\Get-WindowsAutoPilotInfo.ps1 -ComputerName <hostname> -OutputFile .\DeviceID.csv

cd "C:\Program Files\Internet Explorer\"
iexplore.exe (.\iexplore.exe if on PS mode) and send the file via email if not possible to copy the file

